Each time a "Yosenju" monster(s) is Normal or Special Summoned, place 1 Yosen Counter on this card. You can remove Yosen Counters from this card to activate these effects. ● 1 Counter: All "Yosenju" monsters you currently control gain 300 ATK until the end of this turn. (This ATK gain remains even if this card leaves the field.)● 3 Counters: Add 1 "Yosenju" card from your Deck or Graveyard to your hand.You can only use this effect of "Yokai Shrine of Trials" once per turn.
